Electronics category produced maximum revenue.
Weekend sales were significantly higher.
Peak shopping hours were between 5 PM and 7 PM.
""",
    recommendations="""
Increase stock for high-performing products.
Launch targeted promotions during weekends.
Improve staffing during peak hours.
""",
    images=[
        "visualizations/sales_category.png",
        "visualizations/daily_sales.png"
    ]
)